txt.en: The leader of the Woodworker's Guild has asked to craft chairs to fill orders for the reconstruction efforts.
Rebuilding - There is a Shortage of Chairs

'Hello [placeholder]. Everyone is beginning to rebuild and the Woodworker's Guild is committed to helping. We currently have an order for...'

The guild leader checks their invoices.

'...four hundred chairs. Why don't you make three? With every guild member contributing we'll be done in no time at all!'
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nBuild three guild-pattern chairs.
